  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You (Basil) and your 3 other friends decide to go on a camping trip in the Darkwood Forest, It starts off smoothly, but they are ignorant to the horrors waiting for them inside the forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363820/extras/20cb95b948a929b7e9692267474185fc.avif?t=1733509153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363820/extras_big/20cb95b948a929b7e9692267474185fc.avif?t=1733509153 width=800 height=478 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is mostly story centered with most of the game being dialogue and walking with some simple gameplay in between. There are multiple endings to the story, can you get them all?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOUNDTRACK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the music in this game is all made by me for this game and is copyright free.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You (Basil) and your 3 other friends decide to go on a camping trip in the Darkwood Forest, It starts off smoothly, but they are ignorant to the horrors waiting for them inside the forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363820/extras/20cb95b948a929b7e9692267474185fc.avif?t=1733509153\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3363820/extras_big/20cb95b948a929b7e9692267474185fc.avif?t=1733509153 width=800 height=478 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is mostly story centered with most of the game being dialogue and walking with some simple gameplay in between. There are multiple endings to the story, can you get them all?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOUNDTRACK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the music in this game is all made by me for this game and is copyright free.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
